After the dissolution of the limited liability company pursuant to KRS 275.285(2), (3), or (4), the limited liability company shall file articles of dissolution with the Secretary of State which set forth:
The name of the limited liability company;
A statement of the subsection of KRS 275.285 pursuant to which the limited liability company has dissolved;
The effective date, which shall be a date certain, of the dissolution; and
Any other information the members or managers filing the articles of dissolution shall deem proper.
